{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775880713573,"sessionID":"ses_285434e13ffeTcPHfsjy16DQ4a","part":{"id":"prt_d7abd32ef001BRmS0Wal7NNuWD","messageID":"msg_d7abd117700196vEtspm6JkkDe","sessionID":"ses_285434e13ffeTcPHfsjy16DQ4a","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-b0a1eb05d25c4597b942a5605efbcb4d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient Delta Specification\n2: \n3: ## Delta from Base System\n4: \n5: ### New Module: python-sdk/code_interpreter\n6: \n7: This change introduces a new Python SDK module for the CodeInterpreter service.\n8: \n9: ### New Files\n10: \n11: 1. **python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/code_interpreter/client.py**\n12:    - Main CodeInterpreterClient class implementation\n13:    - Session management methods\n14:    - Code execution methods\n15:    - HTTP client wrapper\n16: \n17: 2. **python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/code_interpreter/models.py**\n18:    - Data model definitions (Session, ExecutionResult, ExecutionJob)\n19:    - Enum definitions (SessionStatus, ExecutionStatus)\n20:    - Pydantic models for validation\n21: \n22: 3. **python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/code_interpreter/exceptions.py**\n23:    - Custom exception hierarchy\n24:    - Error messages and error codes\n25: \n26: 4. **python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/code_interpreter/__init__.py**\n27:    - Module exports\n28:    - Public API surface\n29: \n30: ### Dependencies Added\n31: \n32: - **httpx ^0.24.0**: HTTP client for async requests\n33: - **pydantic ^2.0.0**: Data validation and serialization\n34: \n35: ### API Changes\n36: \n37: **New Public API:**\n38: \n39: ```python\n40: from agentcube.sdk import CodeInterpreterClient, Session, ExecutionResult\n41: \n42: client = CodeInterpreterClient(base_url=\"http://localhost:8080\")\n43: session = await client.create_session(workspace_id=\"workspace-123\")\n44: result = await client.execute_code(session.session_id, code=\"print('Hello')\")\n45: ```\n46: \n47: ### Backward Compatibility\n48: \n49: This is a new module with no breaking changes to existing functionality.\n50: \n51: ### Integration Points\n52: \n53: - Uses existing python-sdk infrastructure (if any)\n54: - Follows project coding standards\n55: - Integrates with project testing framework\n56: \n57: ### Configuration Changes\n58: \n59: No configuration changes required in existing components.\n60: \n61: ### Deployment Impact\n62: \n63: - New Python package module\n64: - Requires CodeInterpreter service to be deployed\n65: - No changes to existing services\n\n(End of file - total 65 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient Delta Specification\n\n## Delta from Base System\n\n### New Module: python-sdk/code_interpreter\n\nThis change introduces a new Python SDK module for the CodeInterpreter service.\n\n### New Files\n\n1. **python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/code_interpreter/client.py**\n   - Main CodeInterpreterClient class implementation\n   - Session management methods\n   - Code execution methods\n   - HTTP client wrapper\n\n2. **python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/code_interpreter/models.py**\n   - Data model definitions (Session, ExecutionResult, ExecutionJob)\n   - Enum definitions (SessionStatus, ExecutionStatus)\n   - Pydantic models for validation","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775880713564,"end":1775880713572}}}}
